  delayBetweenMessages: 1
  lines:
  - Ooh I guess that does make sense, border control agents like you would have the
    best skillsets to help them out!
  - "I\u2019m just glad to hear your ok, the government is making such a good effort
    to make everyone feel safe\u2026. "
  - "But it seems they\u2019re doing what\u2019s best for everyone as always! Keeping
    them and any scary information from them out."
  bridgeAfterMessages: 1
  bridgeResponse1: "Having to continue work doesn\u2019t bother me too much knowing
    that I\u2019m helping keep everyone safe, but most of all I\u2019m just glad
    everyone is hopeful."
